## 📱 Responsive Design
The layout adapts smoothly across:
- 📱 **Mobile** (small screens) – single-column layout with a slide-in sidebar menu
- 📟 **Tablet** – adjusted grid and spacing
- 🖥️ **Desktop** – full multi-column layout with horizontal navigation

